{"tid":1556754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」連儂牆手足有野想講","createTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:56:06.000Z","uid":245078,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4b87aa6fbc11555b3c71e22dc0f9f39af8911f","tid":1556754,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:07.000Z","msg":"先說明，我係連儂牆附近住，基本上係屋企望落去會見到少少，大家最近係咪發現連儂牆清得好快呢？因為我發現對家已經固定請左班人係淩晨4點左右去清連儂牆，可能你地會諗撕一貼百，係，無錯，可以係咁，但你知唔知我地一次每人最少會用約200蚊印文宣，幾個鐘時間去貼，但係第二日就比人清左。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外今早清場嘅不明人士仲係旺角連儂牆斬人，我係樓上聽到有人叫救命，話有人斬人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我有個諗法，倒不如我地每人隨身帶一疊Memo貼，行到邊就鍾意貼到邊，固定連儂牆佢就可以請人清姐，我全港每個角落鍾意痴就痴佢吹得我漲嗎？</span>"},{"pid":"3ad11da1681e6520620f2d8dc2f9df5a75e6558b","tid":1556754,"uid":245078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:33.000Z","msg":"自推十下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5cbbbf3d97fe74843a1c9b9145facfb97d73d3","tid":1556754,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:43.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e92c6f0e2fad490b92aa80e026b9c2286d7369bb","tid":1556754,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:38:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b2b039baaa53fd3e3e84887591922e14f87adc3f","tid":1556754,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ecdf74db2d974ab3a6344672e0c8e91ba57e3bce","tid":1556754,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:40:02.000Z","msg":"Burn"},{"pid":"54b3448da0f288df773f03165e318166264eede0","tid":1556754,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"Push"